WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
You train hard. Your system should too.

00:03.000 --> 00:07.000
Plan: open the day, see the work, and start training.

00:07.000 --> 00:11.000
Train: log every set, rep, cardio interval, and rest.

00:11.000 --> 00:15.000
Build: create your routine and keep the plan together.

00:15.000 --> 00:19.000
Review: see sessions, volume, completion, and momentum.

00:19.000 --> 00:23.000
Progress: follow personal records, load, frequency, and history.

00:23.000 --> 00:26.000
One system for routines, live logging, history, and progression.

00:26.000 --> 00:30.000
Fawxzzy Fitness. Train, track, progress.
